Docker container to build ariane core and plugins

/ECHINOPSII must be mounted with an already cloned distrib repo
  * All other repositories will be cloned in this dir
  * zip files will be generated in the artifacts subdirectory of this dir
  * You can change this directory to another one (you need to change the -v option as well as the docker cmd)

/root/.m2 can also be mounted
  * to avoid redownloading dependencies at each build
  * to provide an .m2/settings.xml with nexus credentials (necessary for enterprise builds)

** Examples

docker run --rm \
    -v /HOSTHOME/dev/ECHINOPSII:/ECHINOPSII:rw \
    -v /HOSTHOME/.m2:/root/.m2:rw \
    echinopsii/ariane.buildenv \
    /ECHINOPSII/ariane.community.distrib/distribManager.py -s https://hooks.slack.com/services/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 \
        distpkgr master.SNAPSHOT

docker run --rm \
    -v /HOSTHOME/dev/ECHINOPSII:/ECHINOPSII:rw \
    -v /HOSTHOME/.m2:/root/.m2:rw \
    echinopsii/ariane.buildenv \
    /ECHINOPSII/ariane.community.distrib/distribManager.py -s https://hooks.slack.com/services/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 \
        pluginpkgr ariane.community.plugin.rabbitmq master.SNAPSHOT master.SNAPSHOT


*** For the enterprise we need a user and password, you can either:
  * specify the user on the command line and enter the password interactively with the tty (you will need to docker with -t -i)
  * specify user:password in the user field for non-interactive builds
First example goes with interactive and second with automated

docker run --rm -t -i \
    -v /HOSTHOME/dev/ECHINOPSII:/ECHINOPSII:rw \
    -v /HOSTHOME/.m2:/root/.m2:rw \
    echinopsii/ariane.buildenv \
    /ECHINOPSII/ariane.enterprise.distrib/distribManager.py -s https://hooks.slack.com/services/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 \
        distpkgr lbernail master.SNAPSHOT

docker run --rm \
    -v /HOSTHOME/dev/ECHINOPSII:/ECHINOPSII:rw \
    -v /HOSTHOME/.m2:/root/.m2:rw \
    echinopsii/ariane.buildenv \
    /ECHINOPSII/ariane.enterprise.distrib/distribManager.py -s https://hooks.slack.com/services/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 \
        pluginpkgr jenkins:YHN444rty ariane.enterprise.plugin.tibco.rv master.SNAPSHOT master.SNAPSHOT
    
